      <h1>About Lighthouse Club</h1>
      <p class="updated">What it is · who it's for · what you get</p>

      <h2>What it is</h2>
      <p>Lighthouse Club is a membership community for <strong>Chinese speakers worldwide</strong>. No courses, no hustle-culture pep talks — just thoughtful people bringing their experiences and daily lives together: travel, food, the World Cup, pets, tarot, and lending each other a hand. (Conversations are in Chinese.)</p>
      <p class="slogan-line" style="color:var(--gold-deep)">Lighthouse Club · be each other's light, on the sea of our times.</p>

      <h2>What you get</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Real experience</strong> — first-hand knowledge from people who've been there, more reliable than search.</li>
        <li><strong>Your people</strong> — thoughtful, kind, easy-to-talk-to Chinese speakers around the world.</li>
        <li><strong>Daily life</strong> — World Cup, food, pets, tarot… something fresh and someone to chat with every day.</li>
        <li><strong>A safe space</strong> — no need to perform or keep your guard up.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Where we come from</h2>
      <p>The community was founded by creator Nunu and has been officially operated since 2026 by <a href="https://sync-value.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer">Syncvalue Inc.（シンクバリュー株式会社）</a>, a company registered in Japan — bringing a proper membership system and long-term commitment, while the soul stays the same.</p>

      <h2>How we operate</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Application-based</strong>: every application is reviewed by a human to protect discussion quality and atmosphere.</li>
        <li><strong>Freedom with guidelines</strong>: honest sharing, kind interactions, a sunny atmosphere — see our <a href="/legal/guidelines/">Community Guidelines</a> (Chinese).</li>
        <li><strong>Transparent membership</strong>: public pricing, no auto-charge, stop anytime — see <a href="/en/pricing/">Pricing</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Moderated</strong>: a dedicated team keeps the space safe and welcoming.</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="margin-top:48px"><a class="btn gold" href="/en/apply/">Apply to join →</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
